	</project_license>
	<description>
		<p>
			HyperPlay allows players to carry their MetaMask or WalletConnect wallet overlaid on top of every desktop game. Game developers can request transactions or signatures with a simple REST API call that supports every wallet to manage wallet interactions seamlessly.
		</p>
		<p>
			Main Features:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				Seamless wallet integration with MetaMask, WalletConnect, and more
			</li>
			<li>
				Play Web3 native or browser games and make transactions without leaving the game
			</li>
			<li>
				Have access to your MetaMask Portfolio from the app interface
			</li>
			<li>
				Access Epic and GOG games as well
			</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
